{
  "video_id": "gEXt5RaLvrA",
  "title": "How to stop a world trade war",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 895.0,
      "end_time": 4600.0,
      "text": "These are hard times for free trade."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4600.0,
      "end_time": 7119.0,
      "text": "On the one side, Donald Trump."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7120.0,
      "end_time": 9670.0,
      "text": "He stormed out of the G7 meeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9670.0,
      "end_time": 13270.0,
      "text": "refusing to endorse even the principle of free trade."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13270.0,
      "end_time": 15309.0,
      "text": "In the negotiations over NAFTA, he"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15310.0,
      "end_time": 17410.0,
      "text": "insists on adding clauses that defeat"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 17410.0,
      "end_time": 21280.0,
      "text": "its purpose such as one requiring it to be reagreed"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21280.0,
      "end_time": 22510.0,
      "text": "every five years."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22510.0,
      "end_time": 25220.0,
      "text": "And he has imposed tariffs on steel and aluminium"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25220.0,
      "end_time": 28599.0,
      "text": "on absurd national security grounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28600.0,
      "end_time": 31180.0,
      "text": "On the other side, China."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31180.0,
      "end_time": 35890.0,
      "text": "It uses trade deals as a tool of political hegemony in Asia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35890.0,
      "end_time": 37930.0,
      "text": "tightly controls its internal markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 37930.0,
      "end_time": 41320.0,
      "text": "and extracts intellectual property from foreign firms"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41320.0,
      "end_time": 43420.0,
      "text": "doing business there."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43420.0,
      "end_time": 46300.0,
      "text": "Stuck in the middle there is the EU,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46300.0,
      "end_time": 50440.0,
      "text": "which could become the free trade economic superpower were"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 50440.0,
      "end_time": 53199.0,
      "text": "it not for its internal divisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 53200.0,
      "end_time": 57370.0,
      "text": "How to stop the world from collapsing into a trade war?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57370.0,
      "end_time": 61930.0,
      "text": "Push back, push forward, and be patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61930.0,
      "end_time": 65379.0,
      "text": "Canada, Mexico, and Europe are right to initiate"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65379.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68200.0,
      "text": "retaliatory tariffs against the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68200.0,
      "end_time": 72520.0,
      "text": "Bullying has consequences, and it is especially good"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72520.0,
      "end_time": 76890.0,
      "text": "that these countries are showing a unified front."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76900.0,
      "end_time": 79150.0,
      "text": "But it is equally important that countermeasures"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79150.0,
      "end_time": 80500.0,
      "text": "are proportionate."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80500.0,
      "end_time": 85270.0,
      "text": "They must meet like with like, not escalate."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85270.0,
      "end_time": 86950.0,
      "text": "The same applies to China."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86950.0,
      "end_time": 90730.0,
      "text": "Its tech companies are keen to expand overseas, often"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90730.0,
      "end_time": 92530.0,
      "text": "by buying local companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92530.0,
      "end_time": 95390.0,
      "text": "Regulators should treat these deals with scepticism"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95390.0,
      "end_time": 98620.0,
      "text": "so long as foreign companies operating in China"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98620.0,
      "end_time": 100720.0,
      "text": "are treated unfairly."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100720.0,
      "end_time": 103240.0,
      "text": "Next, push on."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103240.0,
      "end_time": 105130.0,
      "text": "The world should follow the example"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105130.0,
      "end_time": 109149.0,
      "text": "of Japan, which went ahead with the Trans-Pacific Partnership"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109150.0,
      "end_time": 113180.0,
      "text": "trade deal after Mr. Trump abrogated it."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113180.0,
      "end_time": 117860.0,
      "text": "It is especially key that the EU not let issues like immigration"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117860.0,
      "end_time": 120890.0,
      "text": "divide it on its commitment to free trade."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120890.0,
      "end_time": 123100.0,
      "text": "Countries outside of the US and China"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 123100.0,
      "end_time": 125710.0,
      "text": "must keep their own houses clean, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125710.0,
      "end_time": 129340.0,
      "text": "When Mr. Trump complains about dairy protectionism in Canada,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129340.0,
      "end_time": 130600.0,
      "text": "he has a point."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 130720.0,
      "end_time": 132970.0,
      "text": "Finally, be patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132970.0,
      "end_time": 136750.0,
      "text": "The arc of trade history is long."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136750.0,
      "end_time": 142690.0,
      "text": "Even if Mr. Trump wins again, 2024 is not far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142690.0,
      "end_time": 146600.0,
      "text": "The multilateral organisations that push free trade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146600.0,
      "end_time": 150790.0,
      "text": "such as the G7, must be kept going, even under duress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150790.0,
      "end_time": 155230.0,
      "text": "until a new day dawns."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 155230.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "That is the FT view."
    }
  ]
}